      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently 22 degrees and partly cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.548,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.152,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a8aee31737c",
        "a4ca3c262fa"
      ],
      "end": 38.683,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 17.548,
      "text": "NVIDIA is moving telecom operators away from simple task-based automation toward agentic AI. These new agents are designed to run twenty-four seven across network operations, customer care, and back-office workflows. While many operators have already used generative AI for predetermined steps, this shift aims for a higher level of autonomy in critical infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "aa5cfe3fe4c"
      ],
      "end": 59.064,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 38.683,
      "text": "This push for autonomy extends to the tools developers use to build these models. Hugging Face is now shipping updates to its hub Python client every week. The company uses a combination of AI tools and human oversight to accelerate the delivery pipeline for the core library used by thousands of machine learning developers."
    },
    {
      "end": 61.706,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 59.064,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 66.612,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 61.706,
      "text": "This afternoon will be partly cloudy with temperatures between 24 and 29 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 69.631,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 66.612,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 75.67,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 69.631,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 85.482,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
